This paper discusses the limitations of linear or kernel methods in learning, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
